values: I Went shopping today (in ottawa), I'm starting my training in the bar tomorrow. I got a pair a jeans and a clean shirt. any way's I'm working 12 hours tomorrow so I'm going to bed!

So I talked to my boss today, he took it pretty good, I expected worst! So he wont charge me for the storage, good news! Even better, hes maybe going to ask me to be bartender, witch would give me even more cash then the construction job... every thing happen's at the same time. 

Today I learned that it's hard to be a hard worker, because they don't want to let you go when you want to quit!

And the myth about toast alway's falling buttered side down is false! It actually the opposite, when you butter your toast it creates a sort of air pocket on the buttered side, witch will cause it the flip over.

Just so you don't think that I'm a nut case, my journal is mostly use as a bad day reliever.

And if your wondering about what was in that so good message, well I was just talking how I was weirdly offered a job today and how it's gonna suck to be leaving my job right now.

thursday night I went to Carolyne's and Leana's place! of course we got fuck-up!  Every thing was fine until I left...

So I get to the bus stop, wait 15 min for the 95, and then head off home, getting close to down town, I realize that this wasn't the 95 route, so I get off at Rideau to take the right bus! I walk off just to realize that it was the 95 but since I left later from Carolyne's and Leana's place it was the night route!
So since I had 1/2h to wait for the next bus I head-off to go find some where to sit. It was nice there was a band playing in a bar just in front and I could perfectly hear the music. After about 5min a guy walk by and keep's on staring at me curiously, so the guy stop in front of me turns around and lean's on the side of the bus stop! 

The guy sort of look like one of my old friend's that I haven't seen in about 4 years, people have told me that he lost allot of weight and that he was has skinny has me now! but I wasn't sure enough of my self to go and talk to him. So I head out to have a smoke and then the guy lites a smoke, and then he starts walking around in front of me, staring at me again! The band in front started singing Hotel California, and guess what, the guy started singing it out loud...

So the 95 finally arrives, I go and sit in my usual spot in the back and the guy go's and sit down 2 seats from me! And he got off at St-Laurent to! so like I said I was pretty fuck and forgot that it was late so I head to go inside St-Laurent, door's are lock, I get on the escalator and head home, the guy is walking in front of me and he is going straight to my building so he get's in the building we get in the elevator he presses 18, I press 17 and then he starts staring at me again, he finally starts talking to me but all he as to say is "Just so you know St-Laurent is closed after 9 o'clock!"

The fucking guy at the youth center, where I do the web page, didn't want to give me the 3 200$ that he owed me, son of a bitch!

so I called him on friday and we shouted on the phone for about 30 min, I told him that he couldn't pay me the 2 months he owed me with the rest of the 2 500 from the contract, cuz that money goes directly to me! so we shouted and shouted I finally ended up telling him that I would see him in court, scared the shit out of him! so I hang up right in his face.

I called the " Table Jeunesse ", that's the government payed comp. that gives money to young people in quebec to start a business, so any ways  I called there to get some information on what I should do to get the rest of my cash, so the girl there took my number and said she would call me back on thursday and to call the guy at the youth center and tell him that it wasn't in is interest to do what he was doing and all that shit! So I called him, he was so fucking scared his apologized for screaming at me and told me that he would pay me all my cash that he owed me as soon as possible and that until he could get a subvention to pay me for does 2 moths that he owed me that he would borrow it from some one! 

I love being the bad guy! it's a first time felling for me to give shit to some one and then they being so scared that they do everything to pay me what they owe me! it felt great hope to do it again soon!

I never believed in love at first site until now! I have to say that it feel's really weird! There is this girl that comes and eat breakfast once or twice a week, where I work, she is the most beautiful girl I have ever seen in my life, the most perfect thing in the world to my eyes, I would actually give my life just for one date, and I really mean it, even just the chance to go and talk to her would make my world so much better and so much worst at the same time! just to look in to her amazing blue eyes makes my world crumble. Since Ive seen her, I just can't stop thinking about her, I think about her all day at work and when I get home every song I sing reminds me of her( I sing every time I get home for about 2h ). She has stoled my hart away from me, I feel like if Ive just lost every thing! And yes Carolyn and Leana, I feel worst then when I lost Nancy!!! I never thought love could hurt so much...

I'm finally back at my stinky old place!!! feel's nice to be home! I can finally listen to music and smoke inside. I going to go get a bus passe today and get a hair cut, it gets so fucking hot at work with my long hair, and there is so many hot woman where I work, I have to get my chances up! it's going to suck so much having to take the bus to get to work, but it's worth it, with my tips, I make more money working 22h a week then working 40h at Gemma! and I don't even have to make a lunch ( saving so much money ).

I went to the drive-in this weekend, The Day After was playing, it was fucking good! gives me the chill just to think about it. I hope that it was'nt to get us prepared for what myth happen or somme thing, so if you don't want to know how we are going to die in a few years, then don't go see it.

I just got a Electric guitar and a little cheap amplifier!!! I can't wait until I bring it home. It's my dad's, I think he only played once with it, then I was the only one using it! he was going to sell it in the garage sell!!! I ask him how much he wanted for it so he just decided to give it to me!!!

I love my new job! it rocks! I work 4 day's a week and make pretty good money, but I think the best thing is that I finish at 2pm. I will be able to go to night school, but I'm going to go take a Bartender course before, it's 300$ and it's only 3 weekend's, yeah it will suck to take classes on the weekend but I think it's worth it... for the ones that don't know I work in a restaurant, le cafe Mirage bistro, in a government building in hull, Place du Portage. I work with 5 hot girl's and 2 older women! and two of the hot girls are single!!! I mite ask one out on a date this week or next week, depending on the amount of cash I made!

Some one that I can trust enough to tell all my secrets to! Some one that I can take car of when she is sick or cheer up when she is sad!

Can some one please tell me where to find her!!!

well that was my weekend, or most of it!
